14:54.403 --> 14:57.406
And when you said “cap, ” she said “wear”.

14:57.448 --> 15:00.075
Might that be a reference to contraception?

15:02.703 --> 15:04.079
You have quite a flair for this.

15:06.290 --> 15:07.374
