late and the wrong sex.

15:43.786 --> 15:44.953
Don’t be absurd.

16:00.094 --> 16:01.261
‘A’ for Agathe.

16:03.222 --> 16:05.599
Next time I’ll give you a boy.

16:08.185 --> 16:10.688
Can you explain why your
nights have been so bad?

16:17.236 --> 16:18.278
I’m afraid.

16:18.320 --> 16:19.321
Of what?

16:23.075 --> 16:24.702
There’s something in the room.

16:24.743 --> 16:25.452
Something like...

16:27.746 --> 16:30.039
like a cat, only it can speak.

16:30.040 --> 16:31.166
It gets into bed with me.

16:34.670 --> 16:36.171
Last...

16:38.590 --> 16:43.345
last night, it suddenly
whispered something in my ear.

16:43.387 --> 16:44.304
I couldn’t hear what.

16:46.932 --> 16:47.766
But then...

17:01.572 --> 17:04.116
I felt it against my back.

17:05.826 --> 17:09.704
Something slimy like...

17:12.833 --> 17:20.465
like some kind of a mollusc,
moving against my back.

17:24.428 --> 17:25.220
But when I...

17:25.262 --> 17:28.599
when I turned around,
there was nothing there.

17:32.102 --> 17:33.687
You felt it against your back?

17:35.397 --> 17:36.231
Yes.

17:37.483 --> 17:38.400
Were you naked?

17:41.653 --> 17:42.404
I was.

17:43.697 --> 17:44.823
Were you masturbating?

17:49.119 --> 17:50.120
Yes.

17:54.166 --> 17:57.252
Tell me about the first time you can
remember being beaten by your father.

17:59.880 --> 18:04.635
I suppose I was about four.

18:08.681 --> 18:11.016
I’d broken a plate or...

18:12.851 --> 18:14.478
oh, yes, and...

18:15.729 --> 18:24.905
and he told me to go into the little
room and take my clothes off.

18:24.947 --> 18:25.489
And then...

18:29.535 --> 18:37.334
he came in... and spanked me.

18:37.376 --> 18:37.960
And then...

18:40.504 --> 18:45.843
I was so frightened that I
wet myself and then he...

18:47.970 --> 18:49.304
he hit me again.

18:51.765 --> 18:52.891
And then I...

18:55.853 --> 18:59.481
That first time, how did you
feel about what was happening?

19:05.571 --> 19:07.531
<whispering> I liked it.

19:08.991 --> 19:10.367
Would you repeat that, please?

19:10.409 --> 19:11.744
I couldn’t quite hear.

19:14.663 --> 19:16.165
I liked it.

19:20.544 --> 19:21.962
It excited me.

19:25.716 --> 19:27.134
And did you continue to like it?

19:30.763 --> 19:31.847
<crying> Yes!

19:34.600 --> 19:35.351
Yes!

19:38.395 --> 19:44.568
Before long, he only just had to say to me
to go to the little room and I would...

19:47.321 --> 19:48.906
I would start to get wet.

19:54.828 --> 20:02.127
When it came to my brothers or
even just threatened that...

20:04.004 --> 20:05.130
that was enough.

20:05.172 --> 20:06.215
I’d have to go down and...

20:06.256 --> 20:10.094
I wanted to lie down and touch myself.

20:12.137 --> 20:14.223
Later, at school, anything would...

20:14.264 --> 20:20.062
set it off, any kind of humiliation.

20:20.104 --> 20:23.107
I looked for any humiliation.

20:23.148 --> 20:29.446
Even here when you hit
my coat with your stick.

20:29.488 --> 20:34.243
I had to come back right
away, I was so excited.

20:42.960 --> 20:43.794
There’s...

20:46.964 --> 20:48.424
there’s no hope for me.

20:50.134 --> 20:53.134
I’m vile and filthy and corrupt.

20:59.560 --> 21:00.394
I must...

21:02.480 --> 21:04.440
